rows.label: qst700701_msg0001
rows.name:
Ouch... You don't have
to hit me for real!?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0002
rows.name:
Fool! After causing everyone so
much trouble, what are you saying?
Taking detours like a grown-up!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0003
rows.name:
I couldn't help it! I was
being chased by monsters!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0004
rows.name:
Besides, getting all worked up
over a simple garden cleaning
being delayed is so lame.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0005
rows.name: Simple!? What do you mean, simple...!!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0006
rows.name: Nittle-san! Hold back!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0007
rows.name: This is getting complicated!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0008
rows.name:
Idiot! This garden is no
ordinary garden! It is the
garden of the King of Iira.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0009
rows.name: I know that!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0010
rows.name: No, you don't!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0011
rows.name:
A disordered garden evokes the
last war. What good is the king's
garden in such a state!?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0012
rows.name:
Some might be disheartened,
thinking our king can't
even manage his garden.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0013
rows.name:
If the king's prestige is tarnished, it affects
the people's hearts. The end result is chaos,
as it has always been since ancient times!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0014
rows.name:
...No way. Did it have
such a deep meaning?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0015
rows.name:
That's what I've been saying!
It's a thousand years too early
for you to underestimate it!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0016
rows.name: You're amazing, Dad.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0017
rows.name: Even though I don't get it.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0018
rows.name: Still talking back?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0019
rows.name:
No, I mean, because I don't get it,
I want to know, in my own way!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0020
rows.name:
I guess I'll help out a little
more with your work, Dad.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0021
rows.name:
I-I see. If you're going
to say that much...

rows.label: qst700701_msg0022
rows.name:
No! There's more you could give me!
Words of praise! A guide book!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0023
rows.name: I really don't need a beating!!!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0024
rows.name:
Nngh! It's a thousand years
too early for you to have
an opinion on me!!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0025
rows.name:
I'm glad you seem to have
reached an understanding.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0026
rows.name: Is that what you call an understanding?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0027
rows.name:
Yes, because they have
such happy faces.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0028
rows.name: Anyway, I'm glad the garden is clean.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0029
rows.name:
Everyone, thank you! Now I can
give a bright report to the king.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0030
rows.name:
That's wonderful. If there's
anything else we can help with...

rows.label: qst700701_msg0031
rows.name:
Y-You must be joking! Any more of
this and my heart won't take it.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0032
rows.name: Hahahaha.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0033
rows.name: Please live a long life, Nittle-san.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0034
rows.name: Uuuuh, I certainly hope to.
